  "title": "Aurelius, Meditations §aur_06_l: Will either passengers, or patients, find fault and complain, either the one ...",
  "body": "Will either passengers, or patients, find fault and complain, either the one if they be well carried, or the others if well cured? Do they take care for any more than this; the one, that their shipmaster may bring them safe to land, and the other, that their physician may effect their recovery?",
